&book.chapter.clientsideapp;
&book.chapter.widgets;
&book.chapter.gwt;

Vaadin Add-ons




        The Vaadin core library is just the beginning. Vaadin is designed to be
        highly extendable with third-party components, themes, data binding
        implementations, and tools. The add-ons are an important part of the
        Vaadin ecosystem, supporting also different business models for different
        needs.



